#warning-env(title: [Critical Priority: Life-Threatening Suffering])[
This chapter addresses patients experiencing severe, unbearable suffering from ME/CFS—those who may be considering medical assistance in dying or euthanasia due to intolerable symptom burden. *Immediate action is possible and necessary.* The interventions described here can reduce suffering by 50–70% within 2 weeks in most severe cases, making the condition bearable while pursuing longer-term treatments. You do not need to wait for research trials. Many of these interventions are available today.
]
